snippet.title: Gas Hog for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Gas Hog isn't bad...but it's damn close to it.

You can only shoot right, to refuel you have to go down and then going to the upper screen is hard and if you shoot a digit, you will lose a little bit of your score.
